'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #2591] on 10 September 2000 at 12:13:34 pm'!"Change Set:		fasterYetDate:			10 September 2000Author:			Bob Arning- yet another improvement in #worldUnderCursor to avoid expensive calculations"!!DisplayScreen methodsFor: 'other' stamp: 'RAA 9/10/2000 12:12'!morphicWorldAt: aPoint 	| roots outer worldCount |	outer _ self getOuterMorphicWorld ifNil: [^ nil].	worldCount _ 0.	outer allMorphsDo: [ :each | each isWorldMorph ifTrue: [worldCount _ worldCount + 1]].	worldCount < 2 ifTrue: [^outer].	roots _ outer rootMorphsAt: aPoint.	roots isEmpty ifTrue: [^ outer].	^ ((roots first morphsAt: aPoint)		detect: [:each | true]		ifNone: [roots first]) world! !